uest additional documents, such as sales contracts or invoices for inspection.</p></div></div><div id="rlta-3-can-i-open-a-business-account-in-singapore-remotely" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-3-can-i-open-a-business-account-in-singapore-remotely" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="3-can-i-open-a-business-account-in-singapore-remotely" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> 3. Can I open a business account in Singapore remotely?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-3-can-i-open-a-business-account-in-singapore-remotely" aria-labelledby="rlta-3-can-i-open-a-business-account-in-singapore-remotely" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><p>While physical presence is typically required for interviews,Â  you can opt for online interviews with Singapore physical banks or choose fully digital e-banking options. Contact us today for more information</p></div></div><div id="rlta-4-how-many-days-does-it-take-to-open-a-bank-account-for-my-newly-registered-company-in-singapore" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-4-how-many-days-does-it-take-to-open-a-bank-account-for-my-newly-registered-company-in-singapore" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="4-how-many-days-does-it-take-to-open-a-bank-account-for-my-newly-registered-company-in-singapore" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> 4. How many days does it take to open a bank account for my newly registered company in Singapore?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-4-how-many-days-does-it-take-to-open-a-bank-account-for-my-newly-registered-company-in-singapore" aria-labelledby="rlta-4-how-many-days-does-it-take-to-open-a-bank-account-for-my-newly-registered-company-in-singapore" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-